Simple but useful embed Perl for node.js
========================================

SYNOPSIS
--------

    var Perl = require('perl-simple').Perl;
    var perl = new Perl();
    var ret = perl.eval("reverse 'yappo'");
    console.log(ret); // => oppay

Notes
-----

  * perl call is a synchronous.

